    <item>
      <title>如何减少医疗保健对气候的影响？增加远程医疗</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/06/06/nx-s1-4992986/health-care-climate-impact-carbon-telehealth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新研究发现，癌症治疗的远程医疗可以大大减少医疗保健的碳足迹。医疗保健产生了美国 8.5% 的温室气体排放，医学界正在加大努力寻找减少这种影响的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/06/06/nx-s1-4992986/health-care-climate-impact-carbon-telehealth</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
